      </categoryLinks>
      <profiles>
        <profile name="1 Splintermind Combat Drugs" typeId="9b56-9768-f88b-14ac" typeName="Relics" hidden="false" id="935d-461d-d04a-2fcb">
          <characteristics>
            <characteristic name="Description" typeId="becf-f398-aed2-688b">For each attack this unit makes, reroll a Hit Roll of 1 for that attack, and that attack gains Precision.</characteristic>
          </characteristics>
        </profile>
        <profile name="2 Painbringer Combat Drugs" typeId="9b56-9768-f88b-14ac" typeName="Relics" hidden="false" id="f7d6-0e2b-0273-912f">
          <characteristics>
            <characteristic name="Description" typeId="becf-f398-aed2-688b">Add 1 to Resilient rolls for this unit.</characteristic>
          </characteristics>
        </profile>
        <profile name="4 Raider&apos;s Plunder" typeId="9b56-9768-f88b-14ac" typeName="Relics" hidden="false" id="85bd-f188-9dc3-f334">
          <characteristics>
            <characteristic name="Description" typeId="becf-f398-aed2-688b">After this gains this ability, roll 2 D6. Select an ability from your opponent’s army’s ‘Relics’ table equal to the result of one or more of those dice. While this unit has a unique ability from your opponent’s unique abilities table, your opponent cannot select that ability after they secure an objective.</characteristic>
          </characteristics>
        </profile>
        <profile name="6 The Acquiescence" typeId="9b56-9768-f88b-14ac" typeName="Relics" hidden="false" id="b951-4aff-b7bb-4ada">
          <characteristics>
            <characteristic name="Description" typeId="becf-f398-aed2-688b">While enemy units are within 6” of this unit, after each Attacks step, for each of those units with Suppressed 6 and have 6 or less Health remaining among non-leader infantry models, each non-leader infantry model in that unit dies.</characteristic>
          </characteristics>
        </profile>
        <profile name="5 Mask of the First Age" typeId="9b56-9768-f88b-14ac" typeName="Relics" hidden="false" id="dcc9-cf74-17da-7cb6">
          <characteristics>
            <characteristic name="Description" typeId="becf-f398-aed2-688b">While enemy units are within 16” of this unit, each Resolve Test made for those units is worsened by 1.</characteristic>
          </characteristics>
        </profile>
        <profile name="3 Phantasm Grenades" typeId="9b56-9768-f88b-14ac" typeName="Relics" hidden="false" id="1d3c-852e-efd2-e0f5">
          <characteristics>
            <characteristic name="Description" typeId="becf-f398-aed2-688b">After this unit’s Move step, select an enemy unit within 12” of and visible to this unit. Until the End step, for each Resolve Test the selected unit succeeds, it suffers 1 SW. Then, the selected enemy unit suffers 3D6 Suppression.</characteristic>
          </characteristics>
        </profile>
      </profiles>
      <infoLinks>
